"Killing me softly"

1273
01:26:53,378 --> 01:26:55,658
¿Quién coño es ése?

1274
01:26:56,218 --> 01:27:00,537
"Telling my whole life
with his words

1275
01:27:00,658 --> 01:27:06,617
"Killing me softly
with his song

1276
01:27:10,737 --> 01:27:13,977
"I felt all flushed with fever

1277
01:27:14,057 --> 01:27:17,576
"embarrassed by the crowd

1278
