"I felt he found my letters
and read each one out loud

1279
01:27:24,776 --> 01:27:28,256
"I prayed that he would finish

1280
01:27:28,736 --> 01:27:31,535
"but he just kept right on

1281
01:27:31,616 --> 01:27:35,255
"Strumming my pain
with his fingers

1282
